        <updateDate>2007-04-04T18:16:06Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p> Royalty In-Kind for Energy Assistance Improvement Act of 2006 - Amends the Energy Policy Act of 2005, with respect to federal low-income energy assistance programs, to authorize the Secretary of Energy to sell at a discounted price any royalty oil or gas taken in-kind.</p> <p>Requires the discounted price to be at least 50% of the fair market value of the oil or gas.</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
    </summaries>
